Umi-OCR [图片文字识别] https://github.com/hiroi-sora/Umi-OCR
pixpin  [截图的，听说比 snipaste 好用] https://pixpinapp.com/
ScreenToGif  [可以一帧一帧编辑 GIF] https://github.com/NickeManarin/ScreenToGif

